snippet.title: Stargaze - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Stargaze today!
Steam: http://bit.ly/Stargaze_Steam
Viveport:  https://bit.ly/Stargaze_vive

Gaze into the stars as a curious astronomer in this magical VR adventure game. Influence a whole galaxy of planets and their mysterious inhabitants by manipulating a powerful telescope. Take photos of captivating events and fill out your research journal to uncover the secrets of the cosmos. 

Inspired by the "Little Prince" by Antoine de Saint-Exupery
